originalText.text: Dr. Chen was amazing! I felt immediate comfort and trust in him. You can tell he genuinely cares and his evaluation was thorough. I visited his office to treat my neck and back pains. All of his questions and explanations helped me understand why I was in pain and how I could try to prevent it in the future. The treatment itself was fantastic and my pains were relieved after the treatment and then entirely by the next day. I feel great and have peace of mind knowing that if I feel pain again, Dr. Chen will help. Dr. Chen is professional and an expert. I highly recommend Dr. Chen!
